é caracteriza las muñecas de Teresa?</strong></h3><p>Sus muñecas se distinguen por detalles muy particulares: los ojos siempre están cerrados, las bocas tienen forma de corazón —un símbolo Adinkra que, dentro de la cultura Igbo (“akoma”), representa paciencia y tolerancia— y muchas llevan turbantes que evocan una identidad cotidiana y cercana.</p><figure class=\"kg-card kg-gallery-card kg-width-wide\"><div class=\"kg-gallery-container\"><div class=\"kg-gallery-row\"><div class=\"kg-gallery-image\"><img src=\"https://storage.ghost.io/c/0b/21/0b211f14-b12e-4e21-b608-435a1df6692c/content/images/2022/06/Copy-of-DSC_0019_Momentedit.jpg\" width=\"1920\" height=\"1080\" loading=\"lazy\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://storage.ghost.io/c/0b/21/0b211f14-b12e-4e21-b608-435a1df6692c/content/images/size/w600/2022/06/Copy-of-DSC_0019_Momentedit.jpg 600w, https://storage.ghost.io/c/0b/21/0b211f14-b12e-4e21-b608-435a1df6692c/content/images/size/w1000/2022/06/Copy-of-DSC_0019_Momentedit.jpg 1000w, https://storage.ghost.io/c/0b/21/0b211f14-b12e-4e21-b608-435a1df6692c/content/images/size/w1600/2022/06/Copy-of-DSC_0019_Momentedit.jpg 1600w, https://storage.ghost.io/c/0b/21/0b211f14-b12e-4e21-b608-435a1df6692c/content/images/2022/06/Copy-of-DSC_0019_Momentedit.jpg 1920w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 720px) 720px\"></div><div class=\"kg-gallery-image\"><img src=\"https://storage.ghost.io/c/0b/21/0b211f14-b12e-4e21-b608-435a1df6692c/content/images/2022/06/DSC_9900edit.jpg\" width=\"2000\" height=\"1333\" loading=\"lazy\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://storage.ghost.io/c/0b/21/0b211f14-b12e-4e21-b608-435a1df6692c/content/images/size/w600/2022/06/DSC_9900edit.jpg 600w, https://storage.ghost.io/c/0b/21/0b211f14-b12e-4e21-b608-435a1df6692c/content/images/size/w1000/2022/06/DSC_9900edit.jpg 1000w, https://storage.ghost.io/c/0b/21/0b211f14-b12e-4e21-b608-435a1df6692c/content/images/size/w1600/2022/06/DSC_9900edit.jpg 1600w, https://storage.ghost.io/c/0b/21/0b211f14-b12e-4e21-b608-435a1df6692c/content/images/size